WORKOUT PROGRAMS

Worried about whether you have enough time or the right equipment for the workouts? Don’t stress – we've got your back!

TIME REQUIREMENTS

EQUIPMENT REQUIREMENTS

Equipment is always going to be needed for lifting - but we realize many people train from home now and don’t have access to a wide range of equipment… So we’ve also created Home Based Training Programs that can be completed with as little as a set of dumbbells! Not to mention that we’ve also integrated a Substitute Exercise feature - which allows you to quickly change any exercise based off the equipment you have available (or simply to suit your personal preferences).


———————

LIFT with STEPHANIE SANZO


Head Coach Stephanie Sanzo - is well known for her lifting. You can find many examples of her training style online & even access hundreds of free workouts on her social media pages…


But now, for the first time…

You can access her COMPLETE Training Programs - which have been designed to help you build muscle, burn fat, increase your strength and enhance your physique!

We’ll guide you every step of the way and empower you with all the necessary tools & knowledge to get the most out of your training!

This includes…

VIDEO DEMONSTRATIONS


Perfect your form with detailed video demonstrations for each exercise (performed by Stephanie). Never second guess yourself again during your workouts - Stephanie will show you exactly what to do!

Let our algorithm do the heavy lifting. LIFTit calculates how much weight you should lift in your workouts to eliminate all the guesswork!

Witness your results unfold as you track your personal bests as well as your body measurements all in one place. LIFTit records everything and helps you gauge progress and celebrate all the victories along the way.
